text: Yeah, if you're not getting the deck I wouldn't touch that guy for a month or two, I don't think.
Of course, that could backfire too...
I looked up the price trends of Commander product cards. Apparently they are lowest half a year after the products release
And high starters like the extortionist often drop to like 5 bucks
Then again...[[$teferi's protection]]
Definitely the exception there
But it followed the opposite trend, too. Started off fairly cheap.
Even that one was cheapest six months after release
Reprints might be an exception though
Huh. Good to know.
